              &lt;div class="field__item"&gt;&lt;p&gt;(1) Net profit of Rs.5.4 billion up by 76%&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;(2) EBITDA of Rs.22.7 billion up by 34%.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;(3) Revenue of Rs.40.7 billion up by 25%&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;(4) Operating margin of 31% and net margin of 13%&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;(5) Earnings per share of Rs.3.01 up by 76%.&lt;/p&gt;

