  &lt;div class="clearfix text-formatted field field--name-field-announcement field--type-text-with-summary field--label-above"&gt;
    &lt;div class="field__label"&gt;Announcement&lt;/div&gt;
              &lt;div class="field__item"&gt;&lt;p&gt;NTT Communications Corporation, has on the 19th March 2007, informed the Company that they are currently in discussion with Global Telecommunications Holdings N. V. ("GTH") a subsidiary of Usaha Tegas Sdn.Bhd., a business conglomerate headquartered in Malaysia on a possible sell down of part of their holding in SLT to "GTH" and in this regard had sought agreement of SLT for a due deligence exercise to be carried out by GTH of the SLT Group. The Board of SLT has today given their consent for such due deligence exercise.&lt;br /&gt;
Shoji Takahashi&lt;br /&gt;
CEO-SLT&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
          &lt;/div&gt;

